commentPostTextItems.html: That will be it, Gayle finishes it off, Canada has done well, they have put up a fight in both games against the Windies
A very good crowd, lots of youngsters came in after their junior games, that finish early in the morning, we are getting ready for the presentation ceremony
Chris Gayle is Man of the Match for his brilliant 100 today, Rizwan Cheema is Man of the Series. Colin Croft presented the Man of the Match and Man of the Series awards.
This is Gary Grewal signing off, good bye and see you soon!
